alerts.description:
There is a risk of light snowfall (Level 1 of 4).
Precipitation amounts: 1-5 cm; in windward areas: < 10 cm

There is a risk of frost (Level 1 of 2).
Minimum temperature: -1 - -4 °C; local minimum: in valleys and dips > -8 °C

There is a risk of gale-force gusts (Level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 1000 m; Max. gusts: 65-80 km/h; Wind direction: south then south-west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations ~ 90 km/h
There is an increased risk of black ice due to freezing rain (Level 2 of 4).
